headline: Baker Hughes Secures Coiled-Tubing Drilling Deal in Dubai
summary: BKR lands a major coiled-tubing drilling multi-year contract for Dubai's Margham Gas project, strengthening energy security and advancing lower-carbon solutions.

headline: Baker Hughes secures drilling services contract for gas storage project in Dubai
summary: This initiative aims to enhance Dubai's energy stability by improving the system's ability to alternate between natural gas and solar power.
